HEADWORD: Quandary
<hw>Quan"da*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Quandaries</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[Prob. fr. OE.
<ets>wandreth</ets> adversity, perplexity, Icel.
<ets>wandr⟦ae⟧⟦edh⟧i</ets> difficulty, trouble, fr. <ets>vandr</ets>
difficult.]</ety> <def>A state of difficulty or perplexity; doubt;
