HEADWORD: Quandary
<hw>Quan"da*ry</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To bring into a state of
uncertainty, perplexity, or difficulty.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Otway.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

